snippet.title: BackstageOL
snippet.description:
We take you backstage with the biggest names in the world of entertainment every day on the BackstageOL YouTube channel!

Movies. Streaming. Music. Gaming. Tech. We do it all!

Meet the stars of your favorite tv-series and movies. Attend exclusive movie screenings (subscribers only). Get breaking entertainment news as it happens!

Last week Wonder Woman dropped by. Today Liam Neeson. Who could be next?
